    <p>
      INTREACT 2026 aims to bring together global researchers, academicians, educators, innovators, professionals
      and students for two days of knowledge sharing, research presentation and collaborative exploration.
    </p>

    <p>
      Researchers are invited to submit original research papers in interdisciplinary areas including artificial
      intelligence, healthcare, green technologies, education, management, science, social sciences and advanced
      collaborative technologies.
